node.text:
Due to the persistent winds on site, today’s qualifying for Red Bull Hardline has been cancelled. This is to protect the safety of the riders, which remains our absolute priority.
 
We are scheduled to proceed as planned at 2pm BST tomorrow with an extended finals show live on Red Bull TV.
 
Please check our BIO for updates and confirmation.

#redbullhardline #downhill #mtb #downhillmtb #dhlife #mountainbike #bikelife

But why 😳? Because it’s Red Bull Hardline Race Weekend 🔥. Watch the qualifications LIVE on Red Bull TV from 2pm BST onwards 👉 bio.

🚲: @bragevestavik

The toughest Downhill race on the planet is in full swing and we can’t wait for qualifying tomorrow. 🤘 Join us this Saturday and Sunday LIVE on Red Bull TV. 📺

📸: @nathhughesphoto, @saskiadugon, @moonhead_media 🙏

#bike #bikelife #redbullhardline #mtb #mountainbike #mtblife
